Link: http://javasampleapproach.com/java-tutorial/java-8#Functional_Interfaces

* Apply Functional Methods: Ãœbergabe von Methodeninhalt als Parameter
* Methodenreferenz:
  s -> System.out.println(s)
  System.out::println
* Optional Class
  String text = "";
  Optional<String> opText = Optional.isNullable(text);
  opText.ifPresent(System.out::println)
* Reading File:
  try (Stream<String> stream = Files.lines(Paths.get(filePath))) {			
    stream.forEach(System.out::println);
	} catch (IOException e) {}
* Lamda Expressions
  Runnable r = () -> System.out.println("Hello world!");
